      "author": "dimohy",
      "description": "Automatic sync.\n\n- Auto sync on startup: pull remote Slogs changes once when Obsidian finishes loading.\n- Auto push on change: push a synced file to Slogs ~1.5s after it is edited, created, deleted, or renamed (debounced).\n- Auto pull interval (seconds): periodically pull remote changes; set 0 to disable.\n\nAll three are toggleable in plugin settings. Conflicts are surfaced for manual resolution and never silently overwritten.\n\nInstall via Obsidian community plugins or BRAT (https://github.com/dimohy/obsidian-slogs-sync).",
